metadata.name: Hana-chan
metadata.description:
Hanaabu Hana-chan is an indispensable part of "Daughter of Grass".
As a pollinator of various flowers, she introduces us to wonderful grasses and flowers.
She is a little bit slow-paced and mischievous, but she is a cute girl who is hard to hate.
Bunbun~n♪"
